The paper discusses the process of building ontologies, which is a common topic in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and database (cs.DB) research. The focus on collaboration between ontology developers and domain experts suggests a software engineering (cs.SE) perspective. The proposed solution of creating more readable and editable forms of ontologies also relates to information retrieval (cs.IR) and human-computer interaction (cs.HC).
